params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The name of the entry group that contains the entries, which can be provided in URL format. Example: * projects/{project_id}/locations/{location}/entryGroups/{entry_group_id}

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: The maximum number of items to return. Default is 10. Max limit is 1000. Throws an invalid argument for page_size > 1000.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: Token that specifies which page is requested. If empty, the first page is returned.

params.name: data.read_mask
params.description: The fields to return for each Entry. If not set or empty, all fields are returned. For example, setting read_mask to contain only one path "name" will cause ListEntries to return a list of Entries with only "name" field.
